22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20%2413%20billion%20Omnicom-IPG%20megamerger%20reflects%20a%20new%20era%20as%20Big%20Tech%20and%20AI%20upend%20the%20ad%20industry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Wren%20Omnicom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F55263377ecad04cb3cf831ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOmnicom%20CEO%20John%20Wren.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOmnicom%20and%20Interpublic%20Group%20plan%20a%20%2413.25%20billion%20merger%20that%20would%20create%20the%20world's%20largest%20ad-agency%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndustry%20insiders%20say%20the%20deal%20reflects%20an%20ad%20sector%20under%20threat%20from%20Big%20Tech%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20bigger%20company%20could%20have%20more%20leverage%20to%20make%20deals%2C%20but%20job%20cuts%20seem%20inevitable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20ad%20industry%20insiders%2C%20the%20proposed%20merger%20between%20US%20ad%20giants%20Omnicom%20and%20Interpublic%20Group%20represents%20the%20consolidation%20of%20a%20challenged%20sector%20and%20shows%20that%20the%20future%20of%20advertising%20will%20be%20rooted%20in%20data%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20big%20matters%20as%20the%20industry%20wrestles%20with%20disruption%20from%20the%20might%20of%20Big%20Tech%20players%20and%20the%20advent%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%20While%20AI%20could%20make%20their%20offerings%20more%20efficient%2C%20it%20also%20threatens%20to%20displace%20many%20ad%20agency%20services%20and%20the%20prices%20they%20can%20charge%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20reported%20Sunday%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Fadvertising-firms-omnicom-and-interpublic-nearing-merger-that-would-reshape-industry-a2dd2286%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20confirmed%20by%20the%20companies%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20agreement%20would%20create%20a%20company%20with%20combined%20revenues%20of%20more%20than%20%2425%20billion%2C%20based%20on%20last%20year's%20figures.%20The%20%2413.25%20billion%20all-stock%20deal%20would%20merge%20Omnicom's%20creative%20and%20media-buying%20agencies%2C%20such%20as%20BBDO%20and%20Omnicom%20Media%20Group%2C%20with%20IPG's%20McCann%20Worldgroup%20and%20Mediabrands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20would%20create%20an%20entity%20bigger%20than%20Publicis%20Groupe%2C%20which%20has%20the%20largest%20market%20capitalization%20in%20the%20sector.%20Analysts%20expect%20Publicis%20will%20end%20the%20year%20with%20the%20most%20revenue%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20advertising%20company%20is%20the%20sector's%20star%20performer%20and%20has%20outpaced%20rivals%20thanks%20to%20its%20simple%20messaging%20about%20an%20integrated%20set%20of%20services%20and%20as%20multibillion-dollar%20acquisitions%20in%20areas%20like%20data%2C%20IT%20systems%2C%20and%20commerce%20began%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20It%20also%20came%20out%20of%20the%20gate%20early%20on%20AI%2C%20launching%20its%20internal%20%26quot%3BMarcel%26quot%3B%20platform%20in%202018%2C%20long%20before%20generative%20AI%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215261c24-fd47-486c-8511-68cc1a148ea2%5C%22%3EThe%20combined%20company%20seeks%20to%20get%20an%20edge%20in%20AI%2C%20data%2C%20and%20media%20buying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOmnicom-IPG%20will%20be%20hoping%20to%20knock%20Publicis%20off%20the%20top%20spot%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20just%20on%20paper.%20By%20creating%20a%20larger%20company%2C%20Omnicom-IPG%20will%20have%20a%20bigger%20base%20to%20deploy%20data%20or%20technology%20like%20AI%2C%20which%20could%20give%20it%20leverage%20to%20secure%20beneficial%20and%20exclusive%20deals%20with%20partners%20such%20as%20cloud%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20and%20data%20and%20thereby%20data-driven%20marketing%20has%20been%20arguably%20the%20largest%20driver%20of%20differentiation%20and%20growth%20for%20agencies%20for%20some%20time%20now%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20additional%20scale%20is%20being%20able%20to%20leverage%20major%20technology%20investments%20over%20a%20larger%20base%20of%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Simon%20Nicholls%2C%20partner%20at%20the%20advisory%20firm%20GP%20Bullhound%2C%20which%20works%20on%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20within%20the%20ad%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20industry%20insiders%20say%20both%20Omnicom%20and%20IPG's%20investments%20have%20lagged%20behind%20that%20of%20their%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20rival%20minced%20no%20words.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20merger%20of%20two%20drunkards%20leaning%20against%20the%20lamppost%20as%20far%20as%20AI%20is%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20WPP%20CEO%20Martin%20Sorrell%2C%20who%20now%20leads%20the%20digital-marketing%20company%20S4%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BIPG%20Engine%26quot%3B%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20non-exclusive%20partnership%20with%20Adobe%20GenStudio%2C%20while%20Omnicom%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20Omni%20AI%20platform%20doesn't%20lock%20clients%20into%20the%20Omnicom%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%94%20hasn't%20offered%20as%20many%20specifics%20as%20its%20key%20rivals%20have%20about%20how%20much%20it%20is%20investing%20in%20proprietary%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20merger%20could%20reap%20future%20benefits%20for%20the%20pair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThis%20ushers%20in%20not%20just%20a%20new%20era%20of%20scale%2C%20it%20ushers%20in%20the%20opportunity%20to%20invest%20in%20where%20the%20marketplace%20is%20going%2C%20which%20is%20creative%20and%20tech%20powered%20by%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Laura%20Desmond%2C%20an%20ad%20industry%20veteran%20who%20now%20leads%20the%20martech%20company%20Smartly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScale%20is%20also%20crucial%20in%20media%20planning%20and%20buying%2C%20the%20profit%20centers%20of%20most%20agency%20businesses.%20Generally%2C%20the%20more%20client%20ad%20budgets%20you%20control%2C%20the%20more%20leverage%20you%20have%20as%20an%20agency%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20negotiating%20deals%20with%20media%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20bigger%20is%20also%20particularly%20important%20in%20the%20lucrative%20but%20often%20controversial%20practice%20of%20principal-based%20media%20buying%2C%20where%20agencies%20buy%20ad%20inventory%20in%20advance%20and%20sell%20it%20back%20in%20packages%20to%20clients.%20It's%20controversial%20because%20the%20agency%20doesn't%20disclose%20the%20price%20it%20originally%20bought%20the%20media%20to%20the%20advertiser.%20Agencies%20have%20defended%20the%20practice%20because%20they%20say%20it%20still%20drives%20performance%20for%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20brands%20themselves%20are%20often%20pushing%20agencies%20for%20lower%20ad%20prices.%20A%20larger%20advertising%20agency%20would%20have%20a%20bigger%20market%20of%20clients%20to%20resell%20its%20ad%20inventory%20back%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22127fceea-5984-4df6-9be1-619359011da5%5C%22%3EAn%20opportunistic%20deal%20in%20a%20turbulent%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20rationale%20behind%20the%20deal%20is%20opportunistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIPG%20has%20been%20trailing%20rivals%20recently%2C%20having%20lost%20key%20client%20accounts%20like%20Amazon's%20media%20buying%20business%2C%20General%20Motors%2C%20Pfizer%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Coca-Cola.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Omnicom's%20stock%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWren%20is%20a%20wily%20old%20fox%3B%20he's%20no%20fool%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sorrell%2C%20referring%20to%20Omnicom%20CEO%20John%20Wren's%20move%20to%20agree%20on%20the%20deal%20while%20Omnicom%20was%20on%20the%20upswing%20and%20IPG%20was%20floundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWren%20will%20remain%20CEO%20of%20Omnicom%20after%20the%20deal%20closes%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20The%20acquisition%20is%20expected%20to%20close%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202025%2C%20subject%20to%20regulatory%20and%20shareholder%20approvals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bef3812-695d-4f7b-8abe-f2cb454900d6%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20deal%20means%20for%20ad%20agency%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consolidation%20of%20the%20two%20companies%20will%20likely%20lead%20to%20synergies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20job%20cuts.%20Omnicom%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20transaction%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%20%24750%20million%20in%20annual%20cost%20savings.%20The%20research%20firm%20Forrester%20said%20last%20year%20that%20the%20rise%20of%20automation%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forrester.com%2Fpress-newsroom%2Fforrester-agency-ai-workforce-2030%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E33%2C000%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20ad%20agencies%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20even%20fewer%20big%20roles%2C%20and%20lots%20and%20lots%20of%20junior%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20Flock%20Associates'%20Francis%20said%20of%20the%20overall%20ad%20agency%20sector.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20harder%20to%20climb%20the%20career%20ladder.%20Superstar%20creators%20and%20creatives%20will%20also%20be%20in%20demand%2C%20as%20well%20as%20good%20strategists%2C%20in%20all%20disciplines.%20But%2C%20lots%20of%20other%20roles%20will%20become%20diminished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20create%20opportunities%20for%20smaller%20agencies%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20merged%20company%20works%20its%20way%20through%20the%20disruption%20caused%20by%20integration%2C%20egos%20being%20knocked%20out%20of%20joint%20as%20roles%20combine%2C%20and%20potential%20client%20conflicts%20where%20the%20new%20entity%20suddenly%20works%20with%20two%20or%20more%20fierce%20rivals%20in%20the%20same%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20proposed%20deal%20to%20merge%20Omnicom%20with%20Publicis%20Groupe%20a%20decade%20ago%20memorably%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-and-publicis-groupe-call-off-merger-2014-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efell%20apart%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20pair%20couldn't%20agree%20on%20which%20executives%20would%20hold%20key%20positions%2C%20including%20the%20chief%20financial%20officer%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lessons%20learned%20a%20decade%20ago%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20repeated%2C%26quot%3B%20Wren%20said%20on%20a%20call%20with%20analysts%20on%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENimble%20independent%20agencies%20that%20aren't%20encumbered%20with%20legacy%20businesses%20could%20offer%20good%20career%20opportunities%20for%20people%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20complexity%20of%20a%20giant%20network.%20But%20industry%20insiders%20said%20it's%20probably%20not%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20bet%20on%20companies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20pack%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20working%20in%20in-demand%20specialisms%20like%20data%2C%20tech%20integration%2C%20and%20commerce%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20average%20worker%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20all%20about%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Greg%20Paull%2C%20principal%20of%20the%20R3%20marketing%20consultancy.%20%26quot%3BUnless%20you%20are%20in%20a%20creative%20boutique%20like%20Wieden%20%2B%20Kennedy%20or%20Mother%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20clients%20are%20going%20to%20seek%20out%20the%20world's%20largest%20holding%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-ipg-deal-signals-major-shift-ad-agency-market-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733753695000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6756f594a57635a3d24d0b12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-ipg-deal-signals-major-shift-ad-agency-market-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deal%20to%20create%20the%20world's%20biggest%20ad-agency%20company%20reflects%20a%20challenged%20sector%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20scale%2C%20data%2C%20and%20AI%20to%20remain%20competitive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-ipg-deal-signals-major-shift-ad-agency-market-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAttacks%20On%20Religious%20Places%20Regrettable%26quot%3B%3A%20India's%20Plainspeak%20With%20Dhaka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EForeign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20said%20today%20that%20he%20conveyed%20New%20Delhi's%20concerns%20to%20Dhaka%20over%20the%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh.%20In%20a%20meeting%20with%20Bangladeshi%20Foreign%20Adviser%20Mohammad%20Touhid%20Hossain%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20conveyed%20that%20the%20attacks%20on%20religious%20institutions%20and%20places%20of%20worship%20are%20%26quot%3Bregrettable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Misri%20also%20conveyed%20to%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%20that%20India%20wishes%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bpositive%2C%20constructive%2C%20and%20mutually%20beneficial%26quot%3B%20relationship.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%20after%20his%20high-level%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20underlined%20today%20India's%20desire%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20interim%20government%20of%20Bangladesh%20Authority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20issue%20of%20minorities%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20discussed%20recent%20developments%20and%20I%20conveyed%20our%20concerns%20including%20those%20related%20to%20the%20safety%20and%20welfare%20of%20minorities.%20We%20also%20discussed%20regrettable%20incidents%20of%20attacks%20on%20cultural%20and%20religious%20properties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20discussions%20%26quot%3Bfrank%2C%20candid%2C%20and%20constructive%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20said%20the%20discussions%20allowed%20both%20sides%20%26quot%3Bthe%20opportunity%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20our%20ties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20arrived%20in%20Dhaka%20earlier%20today%20for%20a%20day-long%20visit.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20high-level%20meet%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20amid%20strained%20bilateral%20ties%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20Bangladesh's%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Misri%20first%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20his%20counterpart%20-%20foreign%20secretary%20Jashim%20Uddin.%20The%20meeting%20was%20held%20at%20the%20state%20guest%20house%20Padma.%20The%20two%20foreign%20secretaries%20first%20held%20one-on-one%20talks%20and%20then%20a%20formal%20meeting%20was%20held%20where%20delegates%20from%20both%20sides%20were%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20have%20faced%20testing%20times%20since%20the%20ouster%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20after%20a%20massive%20anti-government%20protest%20in%20August.%20Nobel%20laureate%20Mohammad%20Yunus%20took%20over%20as%20Bangladesh's%20Chief%20Adviser%20days%20after%20Ms%20Hasina%20fled%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20both%20countries%20worsened%20after%20multiple%20incidents%20of%20violence%20in%20Bangladesh%20targeting%20the%20Hindu%20minority%20citizens.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20incidents%20of%20mob%20violence%2C%20vandalism%20of%20property%2C%20and%20desecration%20at%20places%20of%20worship%20targeting%20the%20minorities.%20To%20add%20to%20this%2C%20there%20has%20even%20been%20a%20crackdown%20on%20Hindu%20priests%20by%20the%20interim%20government%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Two%20Hindu%20priests%20are%20being%20prosecuted%20and%20there%20are%20concerns%20over%20their%20captivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhaka%20has%20said%20that%20the%20sporadic%20violence%20in%20Bangladesh%20was%20a%20manifestation%20of%20an%20outburst%20of%20anger%20against%20the%20leaders%20and%20activists%20of%20the%20ousted%20Hasina%20regime%20and%20the%20Hindus%20who%20were%20harassed%20were%20related%20to%20her%20Awami%20League%20party%20and%20violence%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20their%20religious%20faith.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733753520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Frjtlapjc_vikram-misri-bangladesh-foreign-adviser-md-touhid-hossain_625x300_09_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fattacks-on-religious-places-regrettable-indian-foreign-secretary-after-high-level-meet-in-dhaka-7207489%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20said%20today%20that%20he%20conveyed%20New%20Delhi's%20concerns%20to%20Dhaka%20over%20the%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fattacks-on-religious-places-regrettable-indian-foreign-secretary-after-high-level-meet-in-dhaka-7207489%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Post-Assad%20Syria%20will%20be%20a%20new%20challenge%20for%20America's%20Middle%20East%20strategy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syrian%20rebels%20on%20a%20tank%20with%20a%20flag.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6756cb13a57635a3d24d06e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESyrian%20rebels%20wave%20an%20Islamist%20flag%20in%20Damascus%20after%20President%20Bashar%20Assad%20fled%20the%20country%20in%20December%202024.%3Cp%3EOMAR%20HAJ%20KADOUR%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERebels%20toppled%20the%20Assad%20regime%20in%20Syria%20after%20a%20brutal%2013-year%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnce%20again%2C%20the%20region's%20power%20dynamics%20have%20been%20dramaticall