20world's%20biggest%20advertising%20and%20marketing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20had%20been%20in%20third%20and%20fourth%20place%2C%20but%20a%20combined%20entity%20will%20eclipse%20both%20London-based%20WPP%20and%20France's%20Publicis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20will%20receive%200.344%20Omnicom%20shares%20for%20each%20Interpublic%20share%20they%20own.%20Omnicom%20shareholders%20will%20own%2060.6%25%20of%20the%20combined%20group.%20The%20deal%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%20annual%20cost%20savings%20of%20%24750%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmnicom%20was%20valued%20at%20about%20%2420%20billion%20at%20Friday's%20close.%20Shares%20fell%203.3%25%20in%20premarket%20trading.%20Interpublic%20was%20worth%20%2410.9%20billion%20and%20its%20stock%20jumped%2015%25%20ahead%20of%20the%20bell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Omnicom%20will%20have%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20staff%20and%20offer%20services%20across%20media%2C%20precision%20marketing%2C%20CRM%2C%20data%2C%20digital%20commerce%2C%20advertising%2C%20healthcare%2C%20public%20relations%20and%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Wren%2C%20CEO%20of%20Omnicom%2C%20said%20the%20acquisition%20creates%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20value%20for%20both%20sets%20of%20shareholders%20by%20combining%20world-class%2C%20highly%20complementary%20data%20and%20technology%20platforms%20enabling%20new%20offerings%20to%20better%20serve%20our%20clients%20and%20drive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20is%20the%20perfect%20time%20to%20bring%20together%20our%20technologies%2C%20capabilities%2C%20talent%20and%20geographic%20footprints%20to%20bring%20clients%20superior%2C%20data-driven%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhilippe%20Krakowsky%2C%20Interpublic's%20CEO%2C%20said%20the%20two%20companies%20had%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20complementary%20offerings%2C%20geographic%20presence%20and%20cultures%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20combined%20group%20would%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Buniquely%20comprehensive%20portfolio%20of%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E