20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20292%20of%20545%20seats.%20The%20two-thirds%20majority%20mark%20stands%20at%20364.%20%C2%A0But%20the%20situation%20could%20be%20dynamic%2C%20since%20the%20majority%20would%20be%20counted%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20members%20present%20and%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20for%20a%20while%2C%20contending%20that%20the%20current%20system%20is%20a%20drain%20on%20time%2C%20money%20and%20effort.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20question%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20declared%20before%20elections%2C%20which%20puts%20brakes%20on%20development%20work%2C%20the%20government%20has%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20called%20the%20idea%20impractical%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20logistical%20challenged%20the%20poll%20commission%20faces%20in%20just%20holding%20the%20state%20elections%20that%20sometimes%20run%20into%20multiple%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simultaneous%20election%20idea%20is%20also%20undemocratic%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kovind%20report%20has%20suggested%20that%20the%20government%20create%20bipartisan%20support%20and%20a%20%C2%A0countrywide%20narrative.%20The%20implementation%20of%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20can%20only%20happen%20after%202029%2C%20the%20report%20has%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733748360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmt366k2o_one-nation-one-election_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-bill-likely-in-this-session-of-parliament-may-be-sent-to-joint-parliamentary-committee-sources-7208435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20launch%20its%20One%20Country%20One%20Election%20project%20and%20can%20introduce%20a%20bill%20in%20parliament%20in%20this%2