ident%20brews%20a%20potential%20war%2C%20because%20the%20Chinese%20government%20believes%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Britain%20planned%20the%20attack.%20However%2C%20the%20truth%20is%20much%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWebb%20and%20Young%20discover%20that%20Trent%20Clark%20(Angus%20Cooper)%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20powerful%20Clark%20crime%20family%20in%20London%2C%20accidentally%20killed%20Ambassador%20Chen%20(Andy%20Cheung)%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20rage.%20The%20high-ranking%20official%20confronts%20Clark%2C%20who%20has%20been%20supplying%20his%20daughter%2C%20Kai-Ming%20(Isabella%20Wei)%2C%20with%20heroin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20pushes%20Chen%20during%20the%20argument%2C%20causing%20him%20to%20fall%20and%20hit%20his%20head%20%E2%80%94%20killing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavies%20and%20his%20associates%20record%20the%20whole%20incident%20and%20plot%20to%20release%20the%20footage%20to%20expose%20the%20Clark%20family%20and%20the%20political%20corruption%20they%20were%20involved%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20Clark%20had%20Davies%20executed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c88e6100-bc72-4ae8-8827-8dee43a55356%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESam%20Young%20kills%20Trent%20Clark%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BBlack%20Doves%2C%26quot%3B%20putting%20a%20target%20on%20his%20own%20back.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221812%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20with%20long%20black%20hair%20in%20a%20green%20coat%20and%20dark%20trousers%20is%20pointing%20a%20gun%20after%20executing%20a%20man%20whose%20body%20is%20lying%20on%20the%20floor%20in%20front%20of%20him.%20The%20dead%20man%20is%20wearing%20a%20blue%20jacket%2C%20brown%20trousers%2C%20and%20a%20green%20wooly%20hat.%20There%20is%20another%20dead%20body%20lying%20next%20to%20him.%20On%20the%20left%20there%20is%20another%20dead%20man%20wearing%20an%20all-black%20suit%20with%20no%20tie.%20Standing%20over%20the%20bodies%20is%20a%20woman%20with%20long%20brown%20hair%20wearing%20long%20burnt-orange%20coat%20and%