ative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20from%20the%20Rajasthan%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20Computer%20Science%20graduate%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20and%20has%20a%20Master's%20in%20Public%20Policy%20from%20Princeton%20University%2C%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20career%20spanning%20over%2033%20years%2C%20Mr%20Malhotra%20has%20worked%20in%20several%20sectors%20including%20power%2C%20finance%20and%20taxation%2C%20information%20technology%2C%20mines%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20was%20appointed%20Revenue%20Secretary%2C%20he%20was%20Secretary%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Financial%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20extensive%20experience%20in%20finance%20and%20taxation%20at%20the%20state%20as%20well%20as%20the%20central%20government%2C%20according%20to%20information%20on%20the%20Department%20of%20Revenue%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20Mr%20Malhotra%20played%20an%20instrumental%20role%20in%20tax%20policy%20formulation%20for%20direct%20and%20indirect%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malhotra%20replaces%20Shaktikanta%20Das%2C%20whose%20tenure%20will%20end%20on%20Tuesday.%20Mr%20Das%20was%20appointed%20the%2025th%20Governor%20of%20the%20RBI%20on%20December%2012%2C%202018%2C%20after%20the%20abrupt%20exit%20of%20his%20predecessor%20Urjit%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%20was%20granted%20an%20extension%20after%20completing%20his%20three-year%20term%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20taking%20charge%20of%20the%20RBI%2C%20Mr%20Das%20provided%20confidence%20to%20the%20market%20shaken%20by%20the%20sudden%20resignation%20of%20Mr%20Patel%20amid%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20RBI%20and%20the%20government%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20surplus%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733746920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ffvqq610o_sanjay-malhotra-ani_625x300_09_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-new