middle-class%20parents%20that%20I%20will%20pursue%20only%20cricket.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20I%20was%20big%20on%20academics.%20My%20parents%20wanted%20me%20to%20do%20well%20in%20the%20game%20as%20well.%20If%20a%20new%20guy%20walks%20into%20the%20MP%20(Madhya%20Pradesh)%20team%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20ask%20him%20is%20%3Cem%3E'padhai%20kar%20rahe%20ho%20ki%20nahi%3F'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(are%20you%20studying%20or%20not%3F).%20Education%20will%20stay%20with%20you%20till%20you%20die%2C%20a%20cricketer%20cannot%20play%20till%2060.%20You%20have%20to%20understand%20that%20there%20is%20a%20shelf%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenkatesh%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20values%20his%20parents%20have%20taught%20him%2C%20feels%20being%20educated%20helps%20in%20making%20the%20right%20decision%20on%20the%20field%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20really%20excel%20in%20life%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20educated.%20Academics%20can%20give%20me%20the%20perfect%20switch-off%20from%20the%20game.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20thinking%20of%20the%20game%20all%20the%20time%2C%20it%20adds%20pressure.%20If%20I%20can%20do%20two%20things%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20will.%20Being%20an%20educated%20person%20helps%20me%20make%20better%20decisions%20on%20the%20field%20as%20well.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20situation%20when%20it%20won't%20be%20just%20about%20the%20skill%20but%20whether%20you%20can%20make%20a%20better%20decision.%20I%20want%20cricketers%20to%20educate%20themselves%20not%20just%20with%20cricketing%20knowledge%2C%20but%20general%20knowledge%20as%20well.%20If%20you%20can%20complete%20your%20graduation%20or%20post-graduation%2C%20you%20definitely%20should.%20I%20am%20pursuing%20my%20PhD%20(finance)%20now.%20You%20will%20be%20interviewing%20me%20as%20Dr%20Venkatesh%20Iyer%20next%20time!%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733745540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvi