36242966%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Refugee%20Crisis%2C%20Kurdistan%20Question%3A%20What's%20Turkey's%20%26quot%3BNew%20Reality%26quot%3B%20In%20Syria%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESyrian%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad's%20regime%20collapsed%20in%20just%2013%20days%20of%20rebel%20offensive%20after%2024%20years%20of%20rule%2C%20leaving%20a%20political%20vacuum%20in%20its%20capital%20Damascus.%20While%20the%20rapid%20downfall%20was%20not%20entirely%20unexpected%2C%20its%20speed%20has%20left%20Turkey%2C%20along%20with%20other%20foreign%20actors%2C%20scrambling%20for%20power.%20Turkey%2C%20now%20the%20dominant%20external%20force%20in%20Syria%2C%20faces%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20reality%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20its%20president%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20now%20a%20new%20reality%20in%20Syria%2C%20politically%20and%20diplomatically.%20And%20Syria%20belongs%20to%20Syrians%20with%20all%20its%20ethnic%2C%20sectarian%20and%20religious%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20Erdogan%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Syria%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20of%20their%20own%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Collapse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20of%20Assad's%20government%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20coordinated%20offensive%20led%20by%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%2C%20an%20armed%20group%20with%20historical%20ties%20to%20al-Qaeda.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20limited%20campaign%20-%20backed%20implicitly%20by%20Turkey%20-%20quickly%20escalated%20into%20a%20full-scale%20assault.%20Within%20days%2C%20major%20cities%20like%20Aleppo%20and%20Hama%20fell%20to%20rebel%20forces%2C%20and%20the%20Syrian%20Army%20retreated%20to%20defensive%20positions%20around%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-bashar-al-assads-fall-means-for-historic-india-syria-relations-7206308%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3EDamascus'%20Nehru%20Street%2C%20Assad's%20Kashmir%20View%3A%20What%20Now%20For%20India-Syria%20Ties%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurkey%2C%20a%20long-time%20backer%20of%20Syrian%20opposition%20forces%2C%20had%20initially%20aimed%20for%20a%20smaller%20operation%20to%20ease%20pressure%20on%20its%20borders%20and%20counter%20Kurdish%20militias%20allied%20with%20the%20Kurdistan%20Workers'%20Party%20or%20PKK.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20sudden%20expansion%20of%20the%20offensive%20caught%20Ankara%20by%20surprise.%20Senior%20officials%20in%20President%20Erdogan's%20administration%20had%20anticipated%20Assad's%20eventual%20fall%20but%20not%20at%20this%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurkey's%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Turkey%20has%20played%20a%20role%20in%20Syria's%20civil%20war%2C%20supporting%20opposition%20forces%20while%20conducting%20its%20own%20military%20operations%20against%20Kurdish%20militias%20in%20northern%20Syria.%20Erdogan's%20government%20has%20sought%20to%20create%20a%20buffer%20zone%20along%20its%20southern%20border%20and%20curb%20the%20ambitions%20of%20Kurdish%20groups%20seeking%20autonomy%20and%20creating%20a%20sovereign%20nation%20called%20Kurdistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swift%20fall%20of%20Aleppo%20and%20Hama%20has%20created%20opportunities%20for%20Ankara%20to%20shape%20post-Assad%20Syria%2C%20but%20it%20also%20raises%20concerns%20about%20instability%2C%20refugee%20flows%2C%20and%20the%20growing%20influence%20of%20HTS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkremlin-says-surprised-by-developments-in-syria-refuses-to-confirm-if-bashar-al-assad-in-russia-7207284%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGot%20Nothing%20To%20Tell%20You%26quot%3B%3A%20Kremlin%20On%20Assad's%20Whereabouts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET