et%20in%20Dhaka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAttacks%20on%20religious%20places%20regrettable%26quot%3B%3A%20Indian%20foreign%20secretary%20after%20high-level%20meet%20in%20Dhaka%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733739660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0tqdmr9g_vikram-misri_625x300_09_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattacks-on-religious-places-regrettable-indian-foreign-secretary-after-high-level-meet-in-dhaka-7207489%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAttacks%20on%20religious%20places%20regrettable%26quot%3B%3A%20Indian%20foreign%20secretary%20after%20high-level%20meet%20in%20Dhaka%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattacks-on-religious-places-regrettable-indian-foreign-secretary-after-high-level-meet-in-dhaka-7207489%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Is%20Fast%20Losing%20Support%20Among%20Allies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fbpuj7hh8_rahul-gandhi-on-haryana-loss_160x120_09_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20ruling%20party%20falls%20short%20of%20its%20own%20majority%20in%20Parliament%20and%20depends%20on%20allies%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20usually%20considered%20vulnerable.%20A%20similar%20situation%20is%20emerging%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20There%20is%20a%20discernible%20expression%20of%20no%20confidence%20in%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20(LoP)%2C%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20partners%2C%20reflected%20in%20both%20their%20behaviour%20and%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LoP%20is%20not%20directly%20elected%20but%20is%20nominated%20by%20the%20Speaker.%20As%20doubts%20grow%20among%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20partners%20about%20the%20Congress%20party's%20ability%20to%20be%20the%20alliance's%20pivot%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20likely%20to%20become%20a%20%E2%80%98lame%20duck'%20LoP%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20without%20the%20active%20support%20of%20his%20allies.%20His%20attempts%20to%20impose%20his%20idiosyncrasies%20on%20fellow%20MPs%20in%20the%20Opposition%20have%20alienated%20major%20allies%20from%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShort-Lived%20Glory%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Narendra%20Modi's%20political%20sheen%20seemed%20to%20be%20getting%20weaker.%20Following%20two%20rounds%20of%20state%20assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20Congress%20suffer%20a%20drubbing%20while%20the%20BJP%20and%20NDA%20made%20a%20remarkable%20recovery%2C%20Modi's%20glitter%20has%20returned%20with%20a%20bang.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20own%20moment%20of%20glory%20came%20after%20June%204%2C%20when%20his%20party's%20strength%20doubled%20and%20he%20was%20recognised%20as%20the%20LoP%20by%20the%20Speaker.%20His%20newfound%20prominence%20continued%20through%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20but%20faded%20after%20the%20Haryana%20elections.%20Maharashtra%20further%20diminished%20his%20standing%2C%20and%20recent%20actions%20by%20allies%20suggest%20that%20the%20glow%20of%20June%204%20has%20all%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20from%20Wayanad%20initially%20energised%20Congress%20workers%2C%20but%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20defined%20role%2C%20she%20seems%20to%20be%20emerging%20as%20little%20more%20than%20an%20extension%20of%20her%20elder%20sibling.%20Rather%20than%20carving%20out%20a%20distinct%20identity%2C%20she%20is%20being%20viewed%20as%20a%20clone%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20She%20has%20begun%20to%20mirror%20his%20style%20of%20addressing%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIA%20Bloc%20May%20Be%20Falling%20Apart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20reliance%20on%20soliloquy%20has%20become%20a%20political%20liability.%20His%20tired%20slogans%E2%80%94%20'Chowkidar%20Chor%20Hai'%2C%20and%20attacks%20on%20Adani-Ambani%E2%80%94failed%20to%20garner%20electoral%20support.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20criticised%20him%20for%20some%20of%20his%20baseless%20remarks%2C%20but%20he%20remains%20undeterred.%20His%20narrative%20of%20the%20Constitution%20being%20in%20danger%20created%20a%20mild%20stir%2C%20helping%20the%20Congress%20almost%20double%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20However%2C%20his%20predominance%20in%20the%20party%20has%20not%20led%20to%20widespread%20acceptance%20of%20his%20leadership%20among%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties.%20He%20was%20appointed%20LoP%20because%20the%20Congress%20holds%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20but%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20yet%20to%20form%20a%20cohesive%20parliamentary%20front.%20The%20alliance%20remains%20limited%20to%20contesting%20some%20elections%20together%2C%20with%20no%20decisive%20leadership.%20A%20Samajwadi%20Party%20spokesman%20recently%20stated%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20%E2%80%9Cnow%20exists%20largely%20in%20the%20media%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20failed%20to%20name%20a%20convenor%20or%20identify%20a%20leader%20after%20a%20year%20of%20discussions.%20Attempts%20by%20non-Congress%20parties%20to%20elevate%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20as%20the%20alliance's%20central%20figure%20were%20met%20with%20cold%20responses%20from%20his%20own%20party%20and%20were%20quickly%20forgotten.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20after%20initially%20suggesting%20the%20name%20of%20the%20bloc%20and%20later%20proposing%20Kharge's%20name%2C%20chose%20to%20go%20solo%2C%20ignoring%20both%20Congress%20and%20the%20CPI(M)%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Trinamool%20not%20only%20increased%20its%20parliamentary%20tally%20but%20also%20retained%20its%20primacy%20in%20recent%20assembly%20by-elections%2C%20positioning%20itself%20as%20the%20dominant%20party%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Rahul%20Is%20Losing%20Support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20June%204%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20aggressive%20stance%20as%20LoP%20in%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20he%20seemed%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20main%20challenger%20to%20Narendra%20Modi.%20However%2C%20recent%20remarks%20by%20Trinamool's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20leader%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20followed%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20assertion%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20run%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%A6%20if%20they%20can't%20run%20the%20show%26quot%3B%2C%20have%20dampened%20his%20prospects.%20The%20support%20of%20figures%20like%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20(SP)%2C%20and%20Tejaswi%20Yadav%20(RJD)%20for%20Mamata's%20leadership%20only%20highlights%20the%20diminishing%20support%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20insistence%20on%20carrying%20on%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20narratives%20has%20caused%20further%20rifts%20in%20the%20opposition.%20MPs%20from%20Trinamool%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20skipped%20Congress-led%20protests%20at%20Parliament's%20Makar%20Dwar%2C%20with%20allies%20feeling%20that%20his%20focus%20on%20personal%20agendas%20prevents%20the%20opposition%20from%20addressing%20more%20pressing%20national%20issues%2C%20as%20the%20House%20is%20disrupted%20endlessly.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhen%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20stopped%20at%20the%20Delhi-Uttar%20Pradesh%20border%20last%20week%20from%20proceeding%20to%20Sambhal%2C%20a%20motley%20group%20of%20around%20200%20Congress%20supporters%E2%80%94reflecting%20the%20party's%20diminished%20capacity%20for%20mass%20mobilisation%E2%80%94protested%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20been%20barred%20from%20performing%20his%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutional%20duty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20LoP%20Post%20Evolved%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20(LoP)%20is%20appointed%20by%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Contrary%20to%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20a%20Constitutional%20post%2C%20the%20LoP%20is%20actually%20a%20statutory%20position%2C%20created%20by%20an%20Act%20of%20Parliament%20in%201977.%20Constitutional%20posts%20are%20those%20established%20by%20the%20Founding%20Fathers%20of%20the%20Republic%20and%20are%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20The%20LoP%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20included%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Parliament%20did%20not%20have%20a%20recognised%20LoP%20until%20the%20Congress%20split%20in%201969.%20The%20Leader%20of%20the%20largest%20Opposition%20party%E2%80%94if%20its%20strength%20exceeds%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20membership%20of%20the%20House%E2%80%94is%20recognised%20by%20the%20Speaker%20as%20LoP.%20The%20Fourth%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20Dr.%20Ramsubhag%20Singh%20of%20Congress(O)%20as%20its%20LoP%20from%20December%2017%2C%201969%2C%20until%20its%20premature%20dissolution%20on%20December%2027%2C%201970.%20The%20Fifth%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%201971%2C%20like%20the%20First%20(1952)%2C%20Second%20(1957)%2C%20and%20Third%20(1962)%20Lok%20Sabhas%2C%20did%20not%20have%20a%20LoP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20of%20LoP%20initially%20emerged%20as%20a%20post%20for%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%20in%20Parliament%20whenever%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20lost%20elections.%20Y.B.%20Chavan%20was%20LoP%20in%201977%2C%20and%20after%20Congress%20split%20that%20year%2C%20C.M.%20Stephen%20became%20LoP.%20There%20were%20no%20LoPs%20in%20the%207th%20and%208th%20Lok%20Sabhas%2C%20the%20last%20Houses%20in%20which%20Congress%20held%20a%20full%20majority.%20The%209th%20Lok%20Sabha%20saw%20defeated%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20as%20LoP.%20After%20that%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20LoPs%2C%20including%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20and%20Sushma%20Swaraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20of%20LoP%20was%20vacant%20in%20the%2016th%20and%2017th%20Lok%20Sabhas%2C%20as%20Congress%20won%20only%2052%20and%2044%20seats%2C%20respectively%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20required%2054-seat%20threshold.%20With%2099%20seats%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20currently%20the%20LoP%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Just%20like%20in%20the%20heydays%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Narendra%20Modi's%20initial%20two%20terms%20also%20saw%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20without%20a%20LoP.%20Now%2C%20with%20allies%20expressing%20doubts%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20ability%20to%20lead%20the%20opposition%20front%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20Modi's%20third%20term%20may%20see%20a%20%E2%80%98lame%20duck%20LoP'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Judgment%20From%20Allahabad%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20political%20circles%20are%20abuzz%20with%20speculation%20regarding%20the%20outcome%20of%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20number%20831%20of%202024%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20for%20hearing%20by%20a%20bench%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20Prayagraj%20on%20December%2019.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20listed%20among%20the%2013%20respondents.%20The%20matter%20was%20previously%20raised%20in%20interviews%20by%20Subramaniam%20Swamy%2C%20and%20December%2019%20will%20mark%20the%20first%20mention%20of%20the%20case%20before%20a%20High%20Court.%20On%20June%2012%2C%201975%2C%20a%20judgment%20from%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20significantly%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20Will%20Allahabad%2C%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20Nehru%20family%2C%20again%20change%20the%20trajectory%20of%20national%20politics%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733738820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fbpuj7hh8_rahul-gandhi-on-haryana-loss_160x120_09_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhi-isolated-amidst-no-confidence-from-allies-7207348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20doubts%20grow%20among%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20partners%20about%20the%20Congress%20partys%20ability%20to%20be%20the%20alliances%20pivot%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20likely%20to%20become%20a%20lame%20duck%20LoP%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20without%20the%20active%20support%20of%20his%20allies%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhi-isolated-amidst-no-confidence-from-allies-7207348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saudi%20Powerhouse%20MBC%20Studios%20Forges%20Landmark%20Multi-Project%20Partnership%20With%20Rising%20Studio%20Telfaz11%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733738643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMBCTELFAZ.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236242981%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saudi-owned%20production%20powerhouse%20MBC%20Studios%20has%20forged%20a%20multi-project%20partnership%20with%20fast%20rising%20Saudi%20studio%20Telefaz11%2C%20the%20label%20behind%20wrestling%20comedy%20%E2%80%9CSattar%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20has%C2%A0scored%20record-breaking%20results%20at%20the%20home%20box%20office.%C2%A0%20Telfaz11%20Studios%2C%20which%20is%20a%20pioneering%20Saudi%20company%2C%20is%20known%20for%20smart%20edgy%20movies.%20Besides%20%E2%80%9CSattar%2C%E2%80%9D%20these%20also%20include%20groundbreaking%20satirical%20drama%20%E2%80%9CMandoob%2C%E2%80%9D%20about%