%20conversations%20gave%20Dipali%20invaluable%20insights%20into%20her%20field%20of%20research%2C%20with%20Manju%20becoming%20one%20of%20her%20greatest%20inspirations%20in%20her%20journey%20to%20preserve%20these%20forgotten%20dishes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20local%20dishes%20are%20disappearing%20in%20Rajasthan%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20seven%20years%2C%20Dipali%20has%20been%20working%20in%20the%20field%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F375518%2Fgovind-bhati-sharon-lok-sangeet-shala-rajasthan-folk-music-jaisalmer-jodhpur-netflix-mismatched-mehman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eart%20and%20cultural%20festival%3C%2Fa%3E%20curation%20across%20the%20country.%20As%20this%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20travelling%20and%20connecting%20with%20people%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%20she%20ended%20up%20noticing%20a%20growing%20trend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20urban%20areas%20were%20succumbing%20to%20the%20convenience%20of%20packaged%20and%20processed%20foods%2C%20rural%20communities%20were%20witnessing%20the%20erosion%20of%20their%20culinary%20traditions.%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20spoke%20to%20a%20woman%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bikaner.%20She%20said%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20feed%20her%20son%20%3Cem%3Ebajre%20ki%20roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread%20made%20out%20of%20pearl%20millets)%20because%20he%20will%20eventually%20move%20to%20the%20city%20and%20if%20people%20see%20him%20eating%20that%20instead%20of%20a%20wheat%20%3Cem%3Echapati%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20they%20might%20make%20fun%20of%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%205103px)%20100vw%2C%205103px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c