p%3EThe%20first%20step%2C%20Sandy%20says%2C%20is%20dissociating%20the%20shame%20that%20is%20attached%20to%20the%20subject%20of%20menstruation.%20Through%20the%20initiative%2C%20he%20envisions%20a%20future%20where%20menstrual%20health%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20taboo%20subject%20in%20India%20but%20instead%20a%20fundamental%20part%20of%20curriculums%20in%20all%20schools%2C%20both%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%E2%80%99s%20keenness%20in%20the%20subject%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20his%20childhood.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20in%20Class%207%2C%20a%20classmate%20of%20mine%20got%20her%20period.%20The%20boys%20did%20not%20know%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20bleeding%20and%20began%20making%20fun%20of%20her%2C%20assuming%20that%20sex%20had%20caused%20her%20to%20bleed.%E2%80%9D%20That%20day%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20Sandy%20made%20his%20way%20back%20home%20with%20a%20question%20for%20his%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20and%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3Enot%20speak%20about%20periods%3F%20Is%20it%20something%20secret%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stereotype%20etched%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284174%2Fmenstruation-periods-girls-school-dropout-whisper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscourse%20around%20menstruation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebecame%20evident%20to%20him.%20So%2C%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20to%20see%20the%20ripples%20of%20Periods%20of%20Pride%20being%20catapulted%20across%20200%20slum%20areas%20in%20over%2026%20cities%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20changemaker%20is%20born%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Sandy%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Khanda.%20His%20childhood%20was%20spent%20helping%20his%20father%20take%20care%20of%20the%20paddy.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Haryana%2C%20he%20would%20often%20hear%20of%20female%20foeticide%2C%20patriarchy%20and%20taboo%20around%20menstrual%20h