E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20ADR%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EADR%20refers%20to%20methods%20of%20settling%20disputes%20without%20resorting%20to%20litigation.%20It%20encompasses%20various%20approaches%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357644%2Fsama-legal-tech-startup-resolves-civil-disputes-through-online-dispute-resolution-odr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediation%2C%20Conciliation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Negotiation%2C%20Lok%20Adalat%2C%20and%20Arbitration.%20These%20methods%20offer%20faster%2C%20more%20flexible%2C%20and%20cost-effective%20alternatives%20to%20conventional%20courtroom%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20JDR%2C%20clients%20depend%20heavily%20on%20advocates%20due%20to%20the%20formalities%20involved%20in%20litigation.%20But%20in%20ADR%2C%20like%20mediation%2C%20the%20processes%20are%20simple%20and%20it%20almost%20resembles%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20system%2C%20where%20both%20the%20parties%20have%20the%20liberty%20to%20talk%20freely%20and%20solve%20their%20disputes%20without%20any%20hostility%2C%E2%80%9D%20A%20G%20Abhishek%2C%20a%20lawyer%20handling%20Supreme%20Court%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20(SLP)%20cases%2C%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EADR%20offers%20numerous%20benefits%2C%20including%20confidentiality%2C%20faster%20resolutions%2C%20and%20tailored%20processes.%20It%20also%20helps%20preserve%20relationships%2C%20often%20strained%20in%20court%20battles.%20ADR%20is%20especially%20effective%20in%20business%2C%20employment%2C%20family%2C%20and%20consumer%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EArbitration%3A%20A%20closer%20look%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArbitration%20is%20a%20formalised%20ADR%20method%20where%20an%20independent%20arbitrator%20hears%20both%20sides%20and%20makes%20a%20decision%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20binding%20for%20both%20parties.%20Think%20of%20the%20arbitrator%20as%20a%20private%20judge%20who%20ensures%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20resolution%20without%20involving%20the%20formal%20court%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%20works%20well%20for%20commercial%2C%20contractual%2C%20financial%2C%20intellectual%20property%2C%20and%20even%20international%20disputes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-500x561.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-500x561.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-267x300.jpeg%20267w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-768x862.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-150x168.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087.jpeg%201140w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386026%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20G%20Abhishek%2C%20a%20lawyer%20handling%20Supreme%20Court%20SLP%20cases%2C%20explains%20that%20ADR%20processes%20almost%20resemble%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20system.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CArbitration%20benefits%20courts%20by%20addressing%20less%20critical%20issues%20outside%20the%20courtroom%2C%20saving%20judicial%20time%20for%20more%20pressing%20cases.%20Consumers%20also%20gain%20quick%20and%20quality%20resolutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20advantages%20have%20prompted%20legislative%20reforms%20aimed%20at%20making%20arbitration%20more%20accessible%20and%20efficient%20in%20India.%20The%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20seeks%20to%20transform%20the%20country%20into%20a%20more%20arbitration-friendly%20jurisdiction.%20By%20reducing%20court%20involvement%20and%20aligning%20Indian%20arbitration%20laws%20with%20international%20standards%2C%20the%20Act%20aims%20to%20create%20a%20more%20efficient%20and%20predictable%20legal%20framework%20for%20resolving%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20characteristics%20of%20arbitration%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Voluntary%20agreement%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EArbitration%20typically%20stems%20from%20mutual%20consent%2C%20outlined%20in%20contracts%20that%20bind%20parties%20to%20settle%20disputes%20through%20arbitration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Neutral%20arbitrator%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20third%20party%20%E2%80%94%20often%20an%20expert%20in%20the%20dispute%E2%80%99s%20subject%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20acts%20as%20an%20impartial%20decision-maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Private%20and%20confidential%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20Unlike%20court%20proceedings%2C%20arbitration%20is%20confidential%20and%20takes%20place%20in%20an%20arbitration%20centre%20which%20protects%20sensitive%20information%20and%20preserves%20business%20reputations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Binding%20decisions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20arbitrator%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20called%20an%20award%2C%20is%20usually%20final%20and%20enforceable%2C%20with%20limited%20grounds%20for%20appeal.%20This%20ensures%20a%20conclusive%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Flexibility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Parties%20can%20tailor%20the%20process%2C%20including%20selecting%20arbitrators%2C%20and%20setting%20rules%20and%20timelines%2C%20making%20it%20faster%20and%20more%20adaptable%20than%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Cost-effective%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arbitration%20often%20reduces%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20prolonged%20court%20battles%2C%20as%20the%20process%20is%20streamlined%20with%20fewer%20procedural%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20International%20applicability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arbitration%20is%20widely%20recognised%20across%20borders%20through%20treaties%20like%20the%20New%20York%20Convention%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20resolving%20international%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20solve%20disputes%20via%20arbitration%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnybody%20who%20has%20mentioned%20in%20the%20agreement%20clause%20that%20their%20disputes%20will%20be%20solved%20via%20arbitration%20can%20approach%20the%20arbitration%20centres.%20The%20agreement%20must%20be%20submitted%20as%20proof%20for%20further%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20parties%20have%20not%20included%20an%20arbitration%20clause%20in%20their%20agreement%2C%20they%20can%20submit%20an%20application%20to%20the%20court%20under%20Section%2011%20of%20the%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20Act%20(1996)%2C%20requesting%20to%20fix%20an%20arbitration.%20Based%20on%20the%20technicalities%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20retired%20judge%20or%20anyone%20with%20equal%20expertise%20will%20be%20appointed%20as%20the%20arbitrator%20for%20the%20dispute%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-1200x675.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDelhi%20International%20Arbitration%20Centre.%20Picture%20source%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dnaindia.com%252Fahmedabad%252Fcolumn-new-avatar-of-arbitration-centre-in-delhi-2769531%26psig%3DAOvVaw1Q_WR53LFoKKxnTFJvgSkD%26ust%3D1732963419825000%26source%3Dimages%26cd%3Dvfe%26opi%3D89978449%26ved%3D0CBQQjRxqGAoTCLCWvfytgYoDFQAAAAAdAAAAABCJAQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDNA%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArbitration%20centres%2C%20often%20established%20under%20High%20Courts%2C%20facilitate%20this%20process.%20Prominent%20examples%20include%20the%20Mumbai%20Centre%20for%20International%20Arbitration%20(MCIA)%2C%20Delhi%20International%20Arbitration%20Centre%20(DIAC)%2C%20and%20Chennai%20Arbitration%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENotable%20cases%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmazon%20vs%20Future%20Retail%20(2020-2023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20and%20Future%20Group%20clashed%20over%20a%20%243.4%20billion%20deal%20for%20Reliance%20to%20acquire%20Future%20Retail%E2%80%99s%20assets%2C%20which%20Amazon%20claimed%20violated%20its%20prior%20agreement%20granting%20rights%20over%20Future%20Group%E2%80%99s%20retail%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Emergency%20Arbitrator%20(EA)%2C%20with%20both%20parties%E2%80%99%20consent%2C%20barred%20FRL%20from%20transferring%20its%20assets%20on%20October%2025%2C%202020.%20FRL%20challenged%20this%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20where%20a%20Single%20Judge%20upheld%20the%20EA%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20but%20the%20Division%20Bench%20later%20deemed%20it%20unenforceable.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20EA%E2%80%99s%20order%20under%20the%20Arbitration%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVodafone%20vs%20Indian%20Government%20(2020)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVodafone%20initiated%20arbitration%20against%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20a%20%E2%82%B922%2C000%20crore%20retrospective%20tax%20demand%20introduced%20by%20a%202012%20amendment%20to%20tax%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%2C%20heard%20at%20the%20Permanent%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20in%20The%20Hague%2C%20concluded%20in%20Vodafone%E2%80%99s%20favour%2C%20ruling%20that%20the%20tax%20demand%20violated%20the%20bilateral%20investment%20treaty%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%20India%20was%20directed%20to%20refund%20legal%20costs%20and%20abandon%20its%20claim%20for%20retrospective%20taxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsumers%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20ADR%20measures%20due%20to%20the%20misconception%20that%20ADR%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20may%20not%20yield%20optimal%20results.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20not%20entirely%20accurate.%20Better%20awareness%20is%20needed%20to%20highlight%20the%20benefits%20of%20these%20measures%20for%20consumers%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20choose%20arbitration%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%E2%80%99s%20legal%20landscape%20evolves%2C%20ADR%20mechanisms%2C%20particularly%20arbitration%2C%20are%20gaining%20traction.%20With%20laws%20like%20the%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20Act%20simplifying%20the%20process%2C%20arbitration%20is%20now%20more%20accessible%20to%20individuals%20and%20businesses%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMediation%2C%20Arbitration%2C%20and%20Lok%20Adalat%20form%20the%20pillar%20of%20reducing%20court%20burden.%E2%80%9D%20Arbitration%20offers%20a%20balanced%20approach%2C%20saving%20time%2C%20preserving%20relationships%2C%20and%20maintaining%20privacy.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20future%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288718%2Ftcs-employee-fights-legal-battle-after-mass-layoff-gets-job-and-salary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edispute%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3